# Title: PAExec Service Installation
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-10-26
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects PAExec service installation
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1569.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/system/service_control_manager/win_system_service_install_paexec.yml

EventID=7045 Provider_Name="Service Control Manager" ServiceName="PAExec-*" OR ImagePath="C:\\WINDOWS\\PAExec-*"